{
  "texts": [
    "Compared with the videoonly reconstruction scheme, their scheme can achieve a three times accuracy improvement.",
    "Nie et al. [256] proposed an AI-based predictive beamforming scheme for multi-modal ISAC systems.",
    "Specifically, they first leveraged the YOLOV5 and FNN to extract the features of vision data and position data, respectively.",
    "Then, a multi-layer perception was utilized to map the fused features to the predicted beam.",
    "Their scheme not only achieved the top-1 accuracy exceeding 60% but also reduced the overhead."
  ]
}